          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;">
      Israel claimed it killed <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #06266D; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-13-jun-25-spotlight-h1-2-top-iranian-military-leaders?source=website" target="_blank">top Iranian military leaders</a>, including IRGC commander Hossein Salami and six nuclear scientists. Israeli PM Benjamin Netanyahu said the operation would continue till Iran pursues uranium enrichment. He also thanked President Trump for confronting Iran's nuclear weapons programme. </p>
         <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;filter:blur(5px);">
